yeah, right
Homonym Number:
Word Class:exclamation
Sense Number:
Definition:an expression of healthy scepticism - a phrase in occasional general use recently re-popularised by a series of beer ads
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
